snippet.title: Jump Space – Ultimate Beginner’s Guide (Top Gameplay Tips You Need to Know!)
snippet.description:
Jump Space has been out in early access for a little over a week and after over 50+ hours in the game, we've picked up loads of gameplay tips you need to know in order to successfully take the fight to the Legion. In this video guide we'll walk you through all the major and minor systems such as components, artifacts, missions, and more so you can have the perfect start in this awesome first person mission based roguelike.

0:00 - Intro
0:25 - What is Jump Space?
2:00 - The Galactic Map & Missions

6:21 - The Hangar & NPCs
7:36 - The Ships
8:53 - Components
12:15 - Materia
13:45 - The Assembler
16:06 - Artifacts
17:10 - Subscribe for More!
